keyFacts: A travel voucher was prepared for a trip related to the U.S. v. Epstein case for witness interviews.
The trip occurred from December 15-17, 2019 to Santa Monica, California.
The trip was associated with case reference 'R20NYS13257 - U.S. v. Epstein'.
The voucher total expenses were $1,360.82 with an estimated trip cost of $1,907.95.
This document shows ongoing investigative activity in the Epstein case as of late 2019.
